# Default: treat everything as text, normalized to LF in the repository
# and on checkout. Windows checkouts of this repo (core.autocrlf=true)
# would otherwise reintroduce CRLF into files with no explicit override --
# confirmed to break a Linux container's #!/bin/bash shebang in
# entrypoint.sh, and to corrupt content-hash provenance checks on HTML/JS/
# JSON files recovered in DEPLOY-GOV-2E. LF is this repository's canonical
# line-ending policy for all text content.
* text=auto eol=lf

# Explicit binary markers -- never run text normalization or diff on these.
*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.webp binary
*.gif binary
*.ico binary
*.mp3 binary
*.mp4 binary
*.wav binary
*.woff binary
*.eot binary
*.ttf binary
*.svg binary

sgf_engine/VENDORED_FROM.txt text eol=lf
